
- Navigation Drawer
    - Spending
    - Income
    - Investments
    ------------------------------
    - Financial stats, info, news
    - Manage notifications (these are to remind the user to enter day's/week's data)
    - Calculator
    - Settings (Currency, app colour etc)


- Today Fragment
   Choice of items: - Enter day's income/spending
                    - Make budget, shopping list, wish list, black list
                    - Add notes

- Week Fragment
   RecyclerView of the days of the week

- Month Fragment
   Calendar




